Nar det hårda foraldralivet hotar deras mentala halsa och aktenskap så bestammer de sig for att ta med barnen på en resa till Skottland till ett stort slaktkalas och for att halsa på Dougs minst sagt knappa pappa Gordie (Billy Connolly). Det som skulle bli en forsoningsresa forvandlas snabbt till ett hysteriskt roligt socialt katastrofområde nar osamja,

programme.title: Big Mommas hus
programme.desc: Agenten Malcolm Turner (Martin Lawrence) jagar en forrymd fånge under tackmantel som storvaxt, besvarlig sydstatsmormor med en attityd som ar lika hårdsmalt som hennes flaskkotletter.

programme.title: Mångalen (Moonstruck)
programme.desc: I denna klassiska romantiska komedi ar en anka från Brooklyn (Cher) redo att gifta om sig. Den har gången planerar hon att gora det ratt, aven om hon måste saga ”ja” till en man hon egentligen inte alskar. Men nar hon blir kar i sin fastmans bror (Nicolas Cage) foljer en romantisk komplikation vardig de storsta komiska operorna! Olympia Dukakis medverkar också.

programme.title: Joe Somebody
programme.desc: Tim Allen ar Joe, en kille vars liv standigt har forandrats till det samre. Nar kontorets mobbare går for långt bestammer sig Joe for att det ar dags att forvandla sig sjalv från ingen till någon.

programme.title: Monte Carlo
programme.desc: Grace (Selena Gomez) ar en vanlig tjej som blir en oavsiktlig prinsessa nar en familjens sommarresa till Paris blir en livs fantasi. Lev som royalty, Grace, tillsammans med hennes två basta vanner, upptacker vem hon verkligen ar - genom att anta en andras identitet.

programme.title: Balls Out: Gary the Tennis Coach
programme.desc: En overentusiastisk vaktmastare på en high-school I USA ger sig på att trana ett gang missanpassade ungdomar for att vinna Nebraska state tennis championship.

programme.title: Disaster Movie
programme.desc: "Disaster movie" foljer de komiska missodena av några sjukt snygga 20-åringar under en odesdiger natt då de forsoker att komma i sakerhet undan alla naturkatastrofer som finns. Asteroider, tornados, jordbavningar och hela alltet, drabbar staden och deras vag då de forsoker losa en rad gåtor for att få ett slut på den okontrollerade forstorelsen.

programme.title: Uptown Girls
programme.desc: Brittany Murphy och Dakota Fanning lyser starkare an alla ljusen i Manhattan i denna underbara New York-saga. Molly (Murphy) ar en festglad prinsessa vars pengar precis tagit slut. Ray (Fanning) ar en kravande nioårig flicka vars senaste barnflicka precis slutat. Nar Rays alltfor upptagna mamma (Heather Locklear) anstaller Molly som Rays nya barnflicka ar det den perfekta chansen for båda flickorna att andra sina vanor och upptacka att ibland kan din basta van komma i den mest ovantade formen!

programme.title: The Happytime Murders
programme.desc: I en varld dar "puppets" lever bland manniskor, men inte riktigt har uppnåt samma status, jobbar detektiv Phil (spelad av Bill Barretta). Han återforenas med sin forna partner, detektiv Connie Edwards (Melissa McCarthy) for att hitta den som mordade detektiv Phils bror och som nu ar ute efter flera ur casten till 80-talets succe-TV-serie The Happytime Gang. Phils gamla tjej (spelad av Elisabeth Banks) har utsatts for hot och ar nasta tilltankta offer. Snart pekar misstankarna mot Phil sjalv. Han sticker och måste nu ensam forsoka losa The happytime murders.

programme.title: Fat Kid Rules The World
programme.desc: Troy Billings ar 17 år, overviktig och ska ta livet av sig. Precis nar han ska hoppa ut framfor en buss raddas han av Marcus, en charmig gatumusiker som har hoppat av high school. En skakig vanskap uppstår mellan de två killarna nar Marcus ber den fullstandigt omusikaliske Troy att bli trummis i ett nytt punkband. Troy tror att det hela mest ar på skoj, men i realiteten ar drivfjadern Marcus stora drom om att bli punkrockvarldens kung, med alla medel som kravs..

programme.title: Nurse Betty
programme.desc: Betty missar aldrig ett avsnitt av sin favoritsåpa A Reason to Love. Efter ett omvalvande mote med två mordare nar hon ser ett avsnitt forvandlas Betty till Syster Betty och ger sig ut på ett uppdrag for att hitta sin stora karlek doktor David Ravell. Folj Betty på hennes vilda och hysteriska resa over landet i sokandet efter hennes dromprins. Men kan Betty hitta honom innan mordaren hittar henne?

programme.title: Wheres The Money
programme.desc: Del ar en snabbtankt ung man från sodra Los Angeles gator. Han får veta att hans pappa, som fortfarande sitter i fangelse, och hans farbror, som precis slappts ut ur fangelse, stal en miljon dollar och gomde det i kallaren till ett gammalt ungkarlshotell. Det ar bara ett problem: En stort universitet håller till i grannskapet och det gamla ungkarlshotellet ar numera ett tillhåll for en studentforening (som ar endast for vita).

programme.title: Next Day Air
programme.desc: Nar en chauffor på villovagar av misstag levererar ett paket som innehåller kokain till fel adress, satter det igång en desperat jakt på kokainet mellan den ursinnige langaren som har skickat det, de skrackslagna avsedda mottagarna som missade det, och de konspirerande oavsiktliga mottagarna som planerar att ta det.

programme.title: Programmet fortsatter strax
programme.desc: Vi tar igen vår skonhetssomn! Stanna kvar for mer prisvard underhållning utvald av Rakuten TV.

programme.title: Off the Rails
programme.desc: Nar deras nara van går bort och lamnar tågbiljetter åt dem ger sig tre kvinnor over femtio ivag for att reprisera sin ungdoms europeiska tågluffaraventyr. Vannen har dock en sista onskan: Att de tar hennes tonåriga dotter med sig. Den har gången upplever de att resan genom Europa ar besvarligare an forra gången. Forsvunna pass, tågstrejker och ovantade romantiska forvecklingar satter vanskapen på spel. Frågan ar: Hinner de i tid for att hedra sin vans minne?

programme.title: Wagons East
programme.desc: De kom for guld, men nu nojer de sig med rinnande vatten. John Candy och Richard Lewis spelar huvudrollerna i denna dråpligt okonventionella blick på den legendariska vastvarlden.

programme.title: Pete Smalls Is Dead
programme.desc: En hollywoodregissor har dott. Hans van KC anar ugglor i mossen och beger sig bakom kulisserna for att ta reda på mer, men hur luskar man reda på sanningen i en stad som forsorjer sig på logner?

programme.title: The Beaver
programme.desc: Walter Blacks humor ar lika svart som hans efternamn. Det går inget bra på jobbet, hans fru har fått nog och hans son hatar honom! Helt under isen - och mitt undersmått suicidal pubrunda - hittar Walter en smutsig handdocka i en sopcontainer. En baver. Med plyschdjuret på handen kan han tala fritt ur hjartat. Och det med brittisk accent till och med! Men samtidigt som Walter återfinner sig sjalv tar hans nya baverpersonlighet snart over helt!

programme.title: Dina, mina och våra (Yours, Mine and Ours)
programme.desc: Dennis Quaid och Rene Russo spelar huvudrollerna i denna harliga nyinspelning av filmen från 1968 med samma namn. En ankeman som ar kustbevakningsamiral och en anka som ar handvaskedesigner blir kara och gifter sig, till stor fortret for hennes 10 och hans 8 barn. Nar barnen planerar att skilja sina foraldrar inser de att det viktigaste ar familjen.

programme.title: Hercules I New York
programme.desc: Forvisad från Mount Olympus skickas Hercules, (Arnold Schwarzenegger), till jorden dar han hittar sann karlek och borjar en lovande karriar som kroppsbyggare.

programme.title: Fast Food Nation
programme.desc: Don Anderson ar marknadsansvarig på Mickey’s, och ligger bakom deras stora succeburgare: The Big One. Nar studier visar att innehållet i burgarna inte ar vad som anges blir Don fundersam, och bestammer sig for att gora besok i hela produktionskedjan. Och vad han upptacker ska visa sig minst sagt omvalvande. Fast Food Nation ar en dramakomedi av Oscarsnominerade Richard Linklater (Boyhood, Bara en natt) med Greg Kinnear (Little Miss Sunshine, Livet från den ljusa sidan) och Bruce Willis (Die Hard, Moonrise Kingdom).

programme.title: Barbershop
programme.desc: Ice Cube, Anthony Anderson, Sean Patrick Thomas, Eve och Cedric the Entertainer spelar huvudrollerna i denna hysteriskt roliga komedi om en barbershop i Chicago dar knivskarp humor aldrig går ur tiden! Calvin (Ice Cube) ar en blivande entreprenor med stora planer... och att driva sin familjs barbershop ar inte en av dem. Men nar han impulsivt saljer butiken till en skum lånehaj inser han snart hur viktig kvartersalongen ar for honom... och hur långt han ar beredd att gå for att få tillbaka den!

programme.title: Mångalen (Moonstruck)
programme.desc: I denna klassiska romantiska komedi ar en anka från Brooklyn (Cher) redo att gifta om sig. Den har gången planerar hon att gora det ratt, aven om hon måste saga ”ja” till en man hon egentligen inte alskar. Men nar hon blir kar i sin fastmans bror (Nicolas Cage) foljer en romantisk komplikation vardig de storsta komiska operorna! Olympia Dukakis medverkar också.

programme.title: Shriek If You Know What I Did Last Friday the 13th
programme.desc: En reporter undersoker en serie mord som kallas Spring Break-massakern, vilket leder till fler illdåd i denna slasherfilmparodi.

programme.title: Next Day Air
programme.desc: Nar en chauffor på villovagar av misstag levererar ett paket som innehåller kokain till fel adress, satter det igång en desperat jakt på kokainet mellan den ursinnige langaren som har skickat det, de skrackslagna avsedda mottagarna som missade det, och de konspirerande oavsiktliga mottagarna som planerar att ta det.

programme.title: Låt de doda vila
programme.desc: Jimmy ar inte bara en fan av heavy metal, skrack, och det ockulta. Han har ett mål: han vill kontakta sin avlidna mamma. Den nya killen i klassen, charmoren Amir, lockar Jimmy till att imponera skolans två snyggaste tjejer, Louise och Anna, med en liten rit. Efter riten inser Jimmy, att han har begått ett forfardligt misstag, som kan grava fram doda hemligheter och betyda hela jordens undergång.

programme.title: 7 Days to Vegas
programme.desc: 7 Days to Vegas is an edgy comedy that is based on a true story of the rise and fall of one of Hollywoods biggest poker games. The names have been changed to protect the guilty. Out of desperation to feed his family, Duke Hamilton, a washed up Hollywood actor in the 90s, starts up a small poker game from his house in the lower-class part of the San Fernando Valley. With the help of his wife KC, the game grows to attract some of the biggest players in the Los Angeles area. These risk-taking guys, who will bet on anything, live life on the edge. Its not just Poker that these spoiled LA moguls bet on.

programme.title: Programmet fortsatter strax
programme.desc: Vi tar igen vår skonhetssomn! Stanna kvar for mer prisvard underhållning utvald av Rakuten TV.

programme.title: West of the Divide
programme.desc: John Wayne stars as Ted Hayden, a tough hombre who goes undercover to join a gang led by a heartless fiend known only as Mr. Gentry (Lloyd Whitlock). Gentry is out to take over a ranch belonging to one of Haydens friends, but as Hayden finds out, Gentry has a lot more than that up his sleeve. Youll have to watch this two-fisted Western to find out the rest!

programme.title: One-Eyed Jacks
programme.desc: Dad Longworth robs a Mexican bank, takes the loot, and leaves his partner Rio to be captured. However, Rio escapes capture and searches for Dad in California.

programme.title: Ghost Town Gold [The Three Mesquiteers]
programme.desc: CAVALIERS OF THE CACTUS COUNTRY--ALWAYS READY FOR A FIGHT OR A FROLICK! The second entry in what would grow into a wildly popular series of Western Three Mesquiteers B-Movies produced by Republic Pictures, Ghost Town Gold tracks the titular trio as they attempt to recover the gold stolen by a gang in its effort to ruin the bank/mayor who ordered them to leave town. Frequent John Wayne collaborator Joseph Kane adds his signature directorial panache to this rousing shoot-em-up, setting the tone for a film series that was so rampantly successful, it spawned 50 sequels and a host of imitators from rival studios.

programme.title: Fighting Fury
programme.desc: A THRILLING TALE OF REVENGE AND REDEMPTION! Based on the story Triple Cross for Danger by the widely lauded Western author Walter J. Coburn, Fighting Fury is a thrilling take on the Western revenge drama. Portraying both a father and his son, star of silent and sound cowboy adventure films, Jack Hoxie (Trouble Busters, Law and Lawless) exudes the classic American rustic charm that still defines the genre. The film spins the yarn of Clay Hill Jr. (Hoxie), a Spanish-American boy raised by a Mexican servant who vows bloody vengeance on three malicious ranchers after they murder his parents and turn his life upside down. Featuring fine supporting performances from genre heavies Helen Holmes,...

programme.title: Red Ryder: Ride, Ryder, Ride!
programme.desc: Red Ryder encounters bandits trying to hold up the stagecoach carrying the owner of the Devils Hole newspaper, Libby Brooks and her brother Gerry. Red successfully drives off the attackers but becomes embroiled in further conflict, leading to a duel that nearly claims his life.

programme.title: With Sitting Bull at the Spirit Lake Massacre
programme.desc: A long-thought-lost film finally surfaces after being unseen for over eight decades. Created and copyrighted by Sunset Productions in 1925 but not released until June 15, 1927, this silent epic features the superior Native American actor Chief Yowlachie (performing here under the name Chief Yowlache) as Sitting Bull. Other fine actors in the cast include the always popular Bryant Washburn and a young Bob Steele, who appears under his real name Bob Bradbury Jr. The story takes place in the 1860s or 1870s near Spirit Lake, Iowa. Settlements of whites are growing in that region but the Sioux Indians also have professed their interest in one such settlement. Chief Sitting Bull surveys the...

programme.title: The Two Gun Man
programme.desc: Ken Maynard stars in this vintage western about ranchers under threat from hired gunmen. Director Phil Rosen, whose career dated back to working with Thomas Edison and included several Charlie Chan features, keeps the action hot with help from a strong ensemble, including Charles King, Murdock MacQuarrie, and a horse named Tarzan! Maynard plays Blackie Weed, a marshall going undercover to capture and arrest some cattle rustlers.He finds himself up against some very bad men, and hes soon framed for murder. Watch as Blackie blazes his way to vindication with a .45 in either hand and the flame of righteous anger in his eyes... Kitty: Nita Martin. Joe Kearney: Lafe McKee. Lem Tolliver: Tom...

programme.title: Cowboy G-Men
programme.desc: In an episode called Koniakers, G-Men Pat Gallagher and Stoney Crockett investigate how U.S. currency in a bank vault was replaced by counterfeit money. Starring Russell Hayden, Jackie Coogan.

programme.title: Cowboy G-Men
programme.desc: Pat Gallagher and his sidekick Stoney Crockett are Secret Service agents in the Old West. In this episode, Pat and Stoney get reports that a man is selling salted mines to investors. The two G-men are determined to discover the truth. Starring Russell Hayden, Jackie Coogan.

programme.title: Petticoat Junction
programme.desc: Uncle Joe is pelted with eggs after his team, the Hooterville Hornets, lose a game. Worse, Bedloe is back in town, which is never a good sign. It turns out Bedloe is planning a suroprise inspection with help frmo the railroad. Uncle Joe Carson: Edgar Buchanan. Betty Jo Bradley: Linda Henning. Kate Bradley: Bea Benaderet. Sam Drucker: Frank Cady. Also starring Pat Woodall and Jeannine Riley. Episode first aired in 1963.

programme.title: Petticoat Junction
programme.desc: Kate hires Herby to work as an assistant manager at the hotel, causing Uncle Joe to fear for his position. Uncle Joe Carson: Edgar Buchanan. Betty Jo Bradley: Linda Henning. Kate Bradley: Bea Benaderet. Sam Drucker: Frank Cady. Also starring Pat Woodall and Jeannine Riley. Series created by Paul Henning. Episode first aired in 1963.

programme.title: Cisco Kid
programme.desc: Cisco and Pancho must prove their innocence when they are accused of killing the assistant to the sheriff in Bonanza.Starring Duncan Renaldo as The Cisco Kid, and Leo Carillo as Pancho. This weekly adventure series was a favorite of the 1950s, following two pals as they traveled the old west, righting wrongs and helping the underdog. The show was produced by ZIV Television, the same company that gave us Highway Patrol and Sea Hunt, and was nominated for a Primetime Emmy in 1951 .This episode aired in 1950.

programme.title: Cisco Kid
programme.desc: Cisco tries to help a beautiful woman prove that her brother is innocent after hes arrested for murder.Starring Duncan Renaldo as The Cisco Kid, and Leo Carillo as Pancho. This weekly adventure series was a favorite of the 1950s, following two pals as they traveled the old west, righting wrongs and helping the underdog. The show was produced by ZIV Television, the same company that gave us Highway Patrol and Sea Hunt, and was nominated for a Primetime Emmy in 1951 This episode first aired in 1950.

programme.title: Stories of the Century
programme.sub-title: S01 : E05 Quantrill and His Raiders
programme.desc: Jim Davis stars as Matt Clark, a railroad detective tasked with the mission to infiltrate the Quantrill gang before the Lawrence Kansas massacre.This western adventure series earned a Primetime Emmy in 1955.. Starring Jim Davis and Mary Castle. Plus, Bruce Bennet stars as Quantrill, with Steve Darrell as Bloody Bill Anderson.

programme.title: Stories of the Century
programme.desc: Detectives Matt and Frankie investigate a woman named Cattle Kate who seems to be the source of cattle ranches suffering major losses in Sweetwater, Wyoming.This western adventure series earned a Primetime Emmy in 1955.. Starring Jim Davis and Mary Castle. Cattle Kate: Jean Parker. Episode first aired in 1954.

programme.title: Judge Roy Bean Collection
programme.desc: In this epsiode, Storts and Hurley are holding hostage a doll that brings good luck to a Mexican village. Starring Edgar Buchanan, Jack Beutel, and Jackie Laughery.

programme.title: Judge Roy Bean Collection
programme.desc: Judge Roy Bean endeavors to exact justice in the small town of Langtry in the Old West. In this episode, a couple of con men attempt to snare Letty into their scheme and spirit her away to San Francisco. Starring Edgar Buchanan, Jack Beutel, and Jackie Laughery.

programme.title: Adventures of Annie Oakley
programme.desc: A member of Teddy Roosevelts Roughriders returns to Diablo to take the valuable land he had been promised. When he arrives, he discovers that the land is part of an Indian reservation. Things quickly turn from bad to worse when a corrupt land agent frames the man for murdering a brave with the hope of inciting an Indian war, which he will use for his own desires for the valuable land. Annie Oakley: Gail Davis, Deputy Craig: Brad Johnson, Tagg Oakley: Jimmy Hawkins. This western adventure series aired from 1954-1957. Cowboy star Gene Autrey was an executive producer for the show, which was nominated for a Primetime Emmy in 1955.

programme.title: Adventures of Annie Oakley
programme.desc: Diablo is in danger when a gang of hired killers comes to town. Lofty finds himself conflicted as he is reluctant to take on the gang once he discovers the leader rescued him back in their days in the U.S. Cavalry. With the state senator possibly the target of the gang, the townspeople call for Lofty to resign amid his reluctance. Annie Oakley: Gail Davis, Deputy Craig: Brad Johnson, Tagg Oakley: Jimmy Hawkins. This western adventure series aired from 1954-1957. Cowboy star Gene Autrey was an executive producer for the show, which was nominated for a Primtetime Emmy in 1955.

programme.title: The Last of the Mohicans
programme.desc: Hawkeye and Chingachcook go up against two thieves with stolen identities. Hawkeye: John Hart. Chingachcook: Lon Chaney Jr. This syndicated series was filmed in Toronto, and was the final project of prolific Hollywood director Sam Newfeild. Based on characters created by James Fenimore Cooper. Episode originally aired in 1957.

programme.title: The Last of the Mohicans
programme.desc: Hawkeye and Chingachcook suspect that a young mans uncle is behind the recent attacks against him. Hawkeye: John Hart. Chingachcook: Lon Chaney Jr. This syndicated series was filmed in Toronto, and was the final project of prolific Hollywood director Sam Newfeild. Based on characters created by James Fenimore Cooper.Episode originally aired in 1957.

programme.title: Bonanza
programme.desc: After Adam gets hurt while saving a woman from a group of indians, the woman must nurse Adam back to health as the rest of the tribe sets out to find her.Starring Michael Landon as Joe, Dan Blocker as Hoss, Lorne Green as Ben, and Pernell Roberts as Adam. This beloved western drama ran for 14 seasons on NBC. Created by David Dortort.

programme.title: Texas Brooklyn and Heaven
programme.desc: When Eddie Tayloe (Guy Madison, 5 Against the House) receives $6,000 from his grandfather, he decides to leave his drab newspaper job and move to New York. His dream is to have a play produced on Broadway. Along the way he picks up a pretty hitchhiker (Diana Lynn, The Miracle of Morgans Creek) who is also leaving her own dreary life for a shot at New York. Unfortunately, they find that the Big Apple is a hard place to make a living. But its also a city where circumstances keep bringing them together!

programme.title: Colorado Sundown
programme.desc: Murder among ranchers is the subject of this Republic Pictures drama. Starring such names as Rex Allen, Slim Pickins, and Chester Clute, this feature was directed by William Whitney. For Trivia Buffs: At one time Whitney was known as the youngest director in Hollywood, having been hired by the newly formed Republic Pictures at the tender age of 21.

programme.title: Captain Apache (Edited Version)
programme.desc: After Harry T. Collier, a beloved commissioner of Indian Affairs, is murdered in late March during the1880s, Captain Apache, an Indian graduate of West Point, is assigned by the army to investigate the crime. Suspecting that O.J., the sheriff of a town bordering the reservation may be involved in the killing, Apache travels there and finds the sheriff dining with his mistress Maude at the Paradise Saloon. Before Apache can question him, however, O.J. abruptly departs and rides out of town with Apache in pursuit. When Apache apprehends him, O.J. swears that he did not kill Collier and relates that the agents dying words were April Morning. Meanwhile, Griffin, a wealthy landowner and six of...

programme.title: Under California Stars
programme.desc: Disaster strikes when Roy Rogerss beloved horse Trigger is stolen and held for ransom money. Will Roy find $100,000 to get his faithful companion back, or will he find a way to trap the gang holding the horse hostage? Along with Roy and Trigger, youll find Andy Devine as Cookie Bullfincher, and young Michael Chapin as Ted Carver, a gallant boy who helps reunite Roy with the smartest horse in show business!

programme.title: The Star Packer
programme.desc: He Dared Death In The Outlaws Lair! John Travers (John Wayne) takes on a mysterious gang leader known as The Shadow in this vintage western from Hollywoods Poverty Row. Director/writer Robert N. Bradbury (Blue Steel, Riders of Destiny) gets the best of a remarkable cast that includes George Gabby Hayes. Of interest to film buffs is that the feature was shot in various California locations by Oscar winning cinematographer Archie Stout (The Quiet Man).

programme.title: Courageous Avenger
programme.desc: Gold, gangs, and the heroic fight for life! Johnny Mack Brown (Billy the Kid, Coquette) stars in this western thriller about murders going on in a mining community. Its a story full of twists, where the greed for gold is only surpassed by the struggle for life!

programme.title: Daughter of the West
programme.desc: A FLAMING PAGE FROM AMERICAN HISTORY Becomes a powerful motion picture...set against the panoramic grandeur of the West!. Martha Vickers stars as Lolita Moreno, a convent raised woman in the 1880s who learns about her Native American heritage through her relationship with an educated Navajo. Morena had been raised at a California mission, but when she leaves to teach school in Arizona, the threads of her mysterious past are revealed. This leads to her involvement with some dangerous people, and a chance to find love in the most unexpected way. The cast includes Phillip Reed, Donald Woods, William Farnum and Milton Kibbee. Pedro de Cordobaa stars as Chief Wykomas.

programme.title: Raiders of Old California
programme.desc: The end of the Mexican-American War finds a brazen U.S. Calvary captain and his men taking over a Spanish land grant. Albert C. Gannaway (The Badge of Marshall Brennan) directs an all-star cast including Jim Davis (Jock Ewing of Dallas), Arleen Whelan (Young Mr. Lincoln) and Lee Van Cleef (The Good, The Bad, and the Ugly). Also, look for appearances by legendary country and western stars Marty Robbins and Faron Young.

programme.title: Red Ryder: Roll, Thunder, Roll!
programme.desc: Red Ryder finds two silver conchas, the trademark of bandit El Conejo, at a raided ranch. He reports the raid to Marshal Bill Faugh but tells him that he suspects that El Conejo, a Robin Hood type character, is being framed.

programme.title: Revenge of the Virgins (Edited Version)
programme.desc: The angry and topless female members of a Native American prepare for battle when white treasure hunters move in on their sacred ground. Peter Perry Jr. (The Secret Sex Lives of Romeo and Juliet) directed this early nudie-cutie from a script by legendary cult filmmaker Ed Wood (Plan Nine from Outer Space). Writing under the pen name Peter LaRoche, Wood churned out this screenplay just before he reinvented himself as the author of seedy adult novels.

programme.title: Stagecoach to Denver
programme.desc: Ride the outlaws highway! Allan Rocky Lane stars as Red Ryder, shootin and fightin his way to justice in this old slugfest from Republic Pictures. This time hes a stagecoach driver battling a crooked land commissioner and his cohorts, including a sheriff on the take. Robert Blake costars as Little Beaver!

programme.title: Abilene Town
programme.desc: Ablaze with guns and guts and glory! Randolph Scott headlines as a star studded cast in this yarn about battling homesteaders. Director Edwin L. Marin (Tall in the Saddle) spins this dramatic post-Civil War tale that takes place in the legendary cow town of Abilene, Kansas, coaxing fine performances from the likes of Ann Dvorak, Edgar Buchanan, Thonda Fleming, and Lloyd Bridges. Saddle up and hang on!

programme.title: Cowboy G-Men
programme.desc: Pat Gallagher and Stoney Crockett are Secret Service agents in the Old West, sent by the government to investigate crimes threatening the young nation. In Mysterious Decoy, Pat and Stony get involved with the famous half-way house that settled the Utah-Arizona boundary. Starring Russell Hayden, Jackie Coogan.

programme.title: Cowboy G-Men
programme.desc: Pat Gallagher and his sidekick Stoney Crockett are Secret Service agents in the Old West, dispatched by the government to investigate crimes threatening the young nation. Starring Russell Hayden, Jackie Coogan. In this episode, the boys rout out Ole Gimpys ghost.

programme.title: Petticoat Junction
programme.desc: Uncle Joe tries to advertise Shady Rest as a hotel for honeymooners.But is Hooterville really the best place for a honeymoon? Uncle Joe Carson: Edgar Buchanan. Betty Jo Bradley: Linda Henning. Kate Bradley: Bea Benaderet. Sam Drucker: Frank Cady. Also starring Pat Woodall and Jeannine Riley. Series created by Paul Henning. Episode first aired in 1963.

Betty Jo Bradley: Linda Henning. Kate Bradley: Bea Benaderet. Sam Drucker: Frank Cady. Series created by Paul Henning. Episode first aired in 1963.

This episode aired in 1950.

programme.title: Cisco Kid
programme.desc: An ex-con is released from prison seeking vengeance against those who put him there. Starring Duncan Renaldo as The Cisco Kid, and Leo Carillo as Pancho. This weekly adventure series was a favorite of the 1950s, following two pals as they traveled the old west, righting wrongs and helping the underdog. The show was produced by ZIV Television, the same company that gave us Highway Patrol and Sea Hunt, and was nominated for a Primetime Emmy in 1951 This episode first aired in 1950.

programme.title: Stories of the Century
programme.desc: Detective Frankie finds herself caught in the middle of a train heist led by the Sam Bass gang.In order to get to Sam, she pretends to be a waitress and flirts with one of his henchmen. This western adventure series earned a Primetime Emmy in 1955..Directed by William Witney. Starring Jim Davis and Mary Castle. Don Haggerty plays Sam Bass, while Denver Pyle is his henchman, Bill Hayes.

programme.title: Stories of the Century
programme.desc: Jim Davis stars as Matt Clark, a detective who faces the notorious gunslinger Johnny Ringo after finding him responsible for a train robbery. Directed by William Witney. Also starring Mary Castle. Donald Curtis, Emlen Davis, Lee Roberts, Harry Lauter, and Ralph Sanford. Directed by William Witney. Episode originally aired March 4, 1954.

programme.title: Judge Roy Bean Collection
programme.desc: In this episode, a Texas Ranger is shot down in cold blood. Determined to bring the killer to justice, the Judge and Jeff turn their focus on Curly, but with a lack of evidence the lawmen are patient until they break the case. Starring Edgar Buchanan, Jack Beutel, and Jackie Laughery.

programme.title: Judge Roy Bean Collection
programme.sub-title: S01 : E22 Luck O The Irish
programme.desc: Judge Roy Bean endeavors to exact justice in the small town of Langtry in the Old West. Starring Edgar Buchanan, Jack Beutel, and Jackie Laughery. In this episode, Judge Roy and Taggart are intrigued by the arrival of Pat OHara and his much younger wife Kate. Pats fondess for drink and gambling has him involved with the towns rowdies who are eying his beautiful bride. The Judge helps sort things out.

programme.title: Adventures of Annie Oakley
programme.desc: Dave Morgan, an honest lawyer, faces off with Carter Holmes, a crooked politician, in a fiery election campaign. Things take a turn for the worse when Holmes attempts to have his opponent killed. Annie Oakley: Gail Davis, Deputy Craig: Brad Johnson, Tagg Oakley: Jimmy Hawkins. This western adventure series aired from 1954-1957. Cowboy star Gene Autrey was an executive producer for the show, which was nominated for a Primetime Emmy Award in 1955.

programme.title: Adventures of Annie Oakley
programme.desc: Looking through an old trunk, Tagg and his friend Johnny Ward, the son of a murdered lawman, find proof that his uncle is an ex-convict and may be involved in a recent bank robbery. Annie Oakley: Gail Davis, Deputy Craig: Brad Johnson, Tagg Oakley: Jimmy Hawkins. This western adventure series aired from 1954-1957. Cowboy star Gene Autrey was an executive producer for the show, which was nominated for a Primetime Emmy Award in 1955.

programme.title: The Last of the Mohicans
programme.desc: A man asserts that he has a Royal Grant that gives him ownership of the entire town.Hawkeye: John Hart. Chingachcook: Lon Chaney Jr. This syndicated series was filmed in Toronto, and was the final project of prolific Hollywood director Sam Newfeild. Based on characters created by James Fenimore Cooper. Episode originally aired in November, 1957.

programme.title: The Last of the Mohicans
programme.desc: A town turns against Eben Cotten as he is accused of selling rifles to the Indians. Hawkeye: John Hart. Chingachcook: Lon Chaney Jr. This syndicated series was filmed in Toronto, and was the final project of prolific Hollywood director Sam Newfeild. Based on characters created by James Fenimore Cooper. Episode originally aired in December, 1957.

programme.title: Bonanza
programme.desc: Little Joe teaches sign language to a beautiful deaf girl, but finds himself in trouble when the girls neighbor becomes jealous of the attention Little Joe is receiving from the girl.Starring Michael Landon as Joe, Dan Blocker as Hoss, Lorne Green as Ben, and Pernell Roberts as Adam. This beloved western drama ran for 14 seasons on NBC. Created by David Dortort.

programme.title: The Gay Cavalier
programme.desc: The Cisco Kid, along with Pancho, try to help an unhappy bride.

programme.title: Boots and Saddles
programme.desc: When a young Englishman inherits a ranch, none other than Gene Autry takes up the challenge of turning the Brit into a real westerner. He convinces the Brit to use the ranch to raise horses, but things quickly grow complicated. Look for the usual cast of characters from Republic Pictures, including Smiley Burnette (as the irresistible Frog Millhouse!). Songs include Take Me Back To My Boots and Saddle, and Ridin the Range.

programme.title: Enemy of the Law
programme.desc: Tex Ritter stars in this western drama about a man who goes undercover to befriend a convict believed to have stolen a shipment of government gold. Also starring Guy Wilkerson as Panhandle Perkins, this offering from Hollywoods Poverty Row features the usual fistfights and entertaining storyline that made these modestly budgeted features well worth watching. Songs include Teach Me To Forget and You Will Have to Pay both sung by Tex!

programme.title: Cry Blood Apache (Edited Version)
programme.desc: An Apache brave seeks vengeance on a band of sadistic gold hunters in this bloody drive-in western. Pitcalin (Jody McRae) leads the marauders who wipe out an Apache camp when they discover gold, only to watch their violent deeds lead to their own demise. Featuring a superb cast that also includes Dan Kemp, Robert Tessier, and Joel McRae, this coldblooded western tale was directed by character actor and filmmaker Jack Starrett (Cleopatra Jones, The Losers).

programme.title: Colorado
programme.desc: Theres trouble out west! Its the Civil War and the Union needs troops back east to defend itself. Roy Rogers stars as Lieutenant Jerry Burke, who is sent to investigate why the returning troops are being stalled in Colorado. Also starring Gabby Hayes, Pauline Moore, and Milburn Stone, this film is action packed with a turn you wont see coming!

programme.title: The Trail Beyond
programme.desc: Rod Drew (John Wayne) is in search of a missing miner and his daughter in this Lone Star Picture. Along the way, Drew rescues his pal Wabbi (Noah Beery Jr.) from card cheats who have framed him for murder. Youll find plenty of action and suspense in this vintage horse opera, originally distributed by the kings of the B western, Monogram Pictures!

programme.title: Death Valley
programme.desc: A love story and a search for gold in the Valley of Death! Dubbed simple, powerful and dramatic by the New York Times on the date of its release, Death Valley is indeed an elegant depiction of love and deception in the American desert during the Gold Rush. In what was to be the final film of famed silent film director Paul Powell (Polyanna), a cast of mostly unknown actors produces uniformly excellent work. Lyrical and graceful, Powells film spins the tale of a young boy who finds love and gold, only to have it stolen from him.

programme.title: High Lonesome
programme.desc: A young drifter is suspected of murder in this stirring production from writer/director Alan Le May (best known for writing The Searchers). John Drew Barrymore stars as Cooncat, a troubled young man who has to steal to survive. With no friends in West Texas, he falls in with some bad customers who involve him in some terrible crimes. The strong cast includes Chill Wills, Jack Elam, and John Archer, with cinematography by Oscar winner W. Howard Greene.

programme.title: Losers End
programme.desc: This spine-tingling drama of the west stars Jack Perrin as a man out for revenge against an outlaw gang. Other stars include Tina Menard as the woman who helps him along the way, and Elias Lazoroff as the daring Don Carlos. Perrin (Jaws of Justice, The Apache Kids Escape), was a familiar face in low budget westerns, his career spanning back to the silent era.

programme.title: W2RC 2025: Rally Raid Portugal Stage 1
programme.desc: Stage 1 of the bp Ultimate Rally Raid Portugal saw fierce battles on a 425 km loop around Grândola. Red Bull KTM’s Daniel Sanders (RallyGP) and Edgar Canet (Rally2) doubled up on their prologue wins, while Thomas Zoldos repeated in Rally3 and Gaëtan Martinez took the quad lead. In cars, Henk Lategan (Toyota) claimed the stage and overall lead ahead of four fellow Toyotas, as Nasser Al Attiyah (Dacia) slipped to eighth after a penalty. Mattias Ekstrom (Challenger) and Alexandre Pinto (SSV) also triumphed. Stage 2 heads into Spain with the week’s longest test: 655 km, including 429 against the clock.

Mattias Ekstrom (Challenger) and Alexandre Pinto (SSV) also triumphed. Stage 2 heads into Spain with the week’s longest test: 655 km, including 429 against the clock.

programme.title: LAT: An Enduring Legacy

programme.title: How Controversy at Imola Changed F1 Forever

In the latest of our new "A Short View Back to the Past" series, Autosports Chief Editor Kevin Turner takes a look at some of the most important moments in Imola’s rollercoaster story.

programme.title: Lindell - Ormbararen - Del 1
programme.desc: Ett från forsta stund fangslande och skakande psykologiskt drama i vilket vansinnets logik driver handlingen mot ett oundvikligt klimax. Det går en seriemordare los i Oslo. For 43-årige nyskilde och nyforalskade Cato Isaksen och hans medarbetare på mordavdelningen vid Oslo-kriminalen blir det en kapplopning med tiden. For mordaren kommer att doda igen. På otackt vis vavs Cato Isaksens privatliv in i irrgångarna i den okande mordarens psyke. Nar det till slut går upp for Cato vem mordaren ar så ar det nastan for sent.

programme.title: Det vita folket
programme.desc: Alex (Vera Vitali) grips på gatan utanfor mataffaren och fors till ett underjordiskt fangelse dar manniskor hålls inlåsta i vantan på deportation. Dar ar Viktoria (Pernilla August) chef och styr med jarnhand. Från sekunden Alex anlander ar hon fast besluten att rymma. Kosta vad det kosta vill. Efter sin hyllade debutfilm ”Apflickorna” ar Lisa Aschan tillbaka med ”Det vita folket”. En dagsaktuell thriller om makt och hierarkier. Skall du ata eller atas?

programme.title: Ljus i skymningen (Lights in the Dusk)
programme.desc: Aki Kaurismakis film om nattvakten Koistinen som forlorar jobbet, friheten och drommarna. Men till sist skonjer han en strimma hopp.

programme.title: De arvlosa
programme.desc: Mika Kaurismaens forsta långfilm. Han skrev manuset tillsammans med sin bror Aki. "De arvlosa" ar en tidlos skildring av hur småskurken Manne, bonddrangen Harri och den vackra Veera kor en Volga genom de forsvinnande finlandska landskapen, med poliser och gangsters standigt på halarna. Den fartfyllda resan ackompanjeras av tidlosa låtar av bland annat Juice och Rauli Badding.

programme.title: Amazon
programme.desc: Den finske mannen Kari (Kari Vaananen) bestemmer seg for å flytte til Brasil med sine to døtre etter kona hans dør. Snart møter han den eventyrlystne amerikanske flygeren Dan (Robert Davi: Die Hard), som forteller Kari om planen sin om å grave etter gull i Amazonas-jungelen. Men Kari møter også den vakre Paola (Rae Dawn Chong: Commando), som lærer ham mer om situasjonen i Amazonas og truslene mot den.

programme.title: Mannen utan minne
programme.desc: Aki Kaurismakis film om en man som tappar sitt minne och får hjalp av fattiga men storhjartade manniskor i en containerby.

programme.title: Skuggor i paradiset
programme.desc: Nikander ar en ensam sopbils-chauffor som en dag moter den anspråkslosa snabbkopskassorskan Ilona. Nikander blir blixtrande kar, men deras omsesidiga blyghet medfor att det romantiska lyser med sin frånvaro. Så plotsligt andras livet… Ilona får sparken och de bestammer sig for att traffas på ett mysigt litet motell. Aki Kaurismaki ar kand for sina socialrealistiska skildringar och svarta karleksforklaringar till ett dystert Finland. Filmer med komiska och omsinta inslag.

programme.title: Moln på drift
programme.desc: Ilona och Lauri ar ett stravsamt par som inte begar mycket av livet. Tak over huvudet, mat på bordet, ett glas vin och en kvall framfor tv-n. De arbetar plikttroget och agnar sina korta ledigheter åt varandra och sin hund. Men en dag hander något som hotar att slå deras trygga tillvaro i spillror. En varm och absurd historia om ett alldeles vanligt par någonstans i Finland.

programme.title: A Polar Year
programme.desc: 28-årige Anders bestammer sig for att resa till Gronland for att undervisa i en liten by. Hans foraldrar tar avstånd från beslutet eftersom de forvantar sig att han ska ta over familjegården, men Anders ser garna ett miljoombyte och nya utmaningar. Livet ar tufft i den lilla byn – tuffare an Anders hade forestallt sig. Byborna tar till en borjan inte emot honom val och om han ska gora sig några forhoppningar om att hjalpa familjerna – inte minst barnen – måste Anders ta ett viktigt beslut. Han måste lara kanna byns manniskor och inte minst deras traditioner. Forst nar han gjort det kommer en helt ny varld att oppna sig for Anders...

programme.title: Pax
programme.desc: En flygmotor exploderar, och planet stortar mot marken. Mycket tyder på att detta ar slutet for alla ombord. Men for några av dem ar det en ny borjan. I luften mellan Stockholm och Oslo foljer vi sju personer och ett hjarta på vag från en kropp till en annan. Nar den tunga maskinen faller ser de livet i ett annat ljus. Aldrig ar livet så narvarande som nar slutet narmar sig. I detta storslagna, romantiska och nargångna dramas ensemble finns flera av Sveriges mest namnkunniga skådespelare, bland annat Samuel Froler, Thomas von Bromssen, Bjorn Granath, Annika Hallin och Marika Lagercrantz.

programme.title: Ettor and Nollor - Del 2
programme.desc: FBI och Interpol får nys om en stor kreditkortsharva och pundaren Sebbe plockas in som misstankt. Nar polisen borjar sina forhor får de hora en otrolig historia från Goteborgs undre varld. Svenska och ryska gangsters, marockanska hackers, korrupta politiker och giriga kostymnissar - alla vill tjana stora pengen, ingen vill vara hunden...

programme.title: Long Story Short
programme.desc: Det har ar berattelsen om Ellen och hennes vanner, och deras mer eller mindre sjalvforvållat komplicerade karleksliv och romantiska drommar. Tre år av vannernas basta och samsta karlekshistorier sammanfattas och berattas genom åtta kapitel, som alla utspelar sig vid olika festliga tillstallningar. Gruppen kampar med iden om det perfekta forhållandet och måste omvardera vad sann karlek egentligen ar.

programme.title: Calamari Union
programme.desc: Sjutton unga man, varav sexton heter Frank och bar svarta glasogon, lamnar en elandig arbetarmiljo och beger sig ut på en farlig resa genom storstaden på jakt efter den mytiska stadsdelen Eira. På grund av olika omstandigheter kommer bara två av dem fram. Men Eira ar inte riktigt det de hoppats på och deras sokande fortsatter – nu i en roddbåt mot Estland… Denna surrealistiska komedi ar Kaurismakis andra långfilm. En skon och absurd berattelse som blandar amerikansk gangsterfilm med finsk punk.

programme.title: Lindell - Sorgmanteln - Del 2
programme.desc: Fyra små flickor på ett fotografi. Tjugo år senare hittas en av dem mordad. En annan ar spårlost forsvunnen. Cato Isaksen ar redo att losa nya kriminalgåtor. Lise Sommer blir upphunnen av sitt forflutna. Hennes basta van Esther Synnøve Lønn har hittats mordad med avskuren hals. Några dagar senare forsvinner Esthers son. Nar polisen borjar att skrapa på ytan visar det sig att en barndomsvan till Lise och Esther Synnøve också saknas. Forhållandet mellan vaninnorna doljer morka understrommar. Vad var det egentligen som hande nar flickorna var små? Och deras mammor - vad doljer de?

programme.title: Flickan från tandsticksfabriken
programme.desc: Iris ar trott på sitt dodstråkiga jobb och liv. For att pigga upp stamningen beger hon sig ut på stan och shoppar en rod klanning. Natten spenderar hon med en rik man som lamnar henne en summa pengar morgonen efter. En tid senare upptacker Iris att hon ar gravid och upplyser den formogne mannen om sin situation, han skickar en ny bunt sedlar och ber henne att gora abort. Då går Iris ut och koper en stor mangd råttgift.

programme.title: 30:e november
programme.desc: Adam och hans polare spenderar sin tid med att trakassera invandrare som de hatar. Men så moter Adam Julia från Peru och de blir blixtforalskad, eftersom varken Adams vanner eller Julias familj skulle acceptera att de två ar tillsammans tvingas de hålla sin karlek hemlig. På Sveriges nationaldag drabbas Adam och hans gang samman med Julias bror, Sascha, och hans vanner. Det hela slutar med att två dodads.

programme.title: Rosso
programme.desc: Rosso, som skickligt kombinerar roadmovie och kriminaldrama, ar berattelsen om den sicilianska lonnmordaren Giancarlo Rosso, som har kommit till Finland for att leta efter sitt nasta mål, som råkar vara hans alskade Marja. Ovantat får Rosso hjalp med spårningen av Marjas bror Martti, trots att de inte ens delar ett gemensamt språk. På resan ingår både skrotningsuppdrag och några rån...

programme.title: Zombie och spoktåget
programme.desc: Zombie (Silu Seppala: Leningrad Cowboys) ar en individ som går sin egen vag och inte kan folja de normer som det finska samhallet har satt for honom. Zombie beslutar sig for att lamna allt och ge sig utomlands - till en plats dar ingen forvantar sig något av honom. Zombie och spoktåget betraktas av många som några av Mika Kaurismakis basta filmer. Filmen belonades med Jussi-priset for Basta regissor, Basta manliga huvudroll och Basta foto år 1992. Tragikomiskt och aven surrealistiskt foljer Zombie med bland andra Mato Valtonen och Sakke Jarvenpaa från Sleepy Sleepers, samt naturligtvis Matti Pellonpaa.

programme.title: Varg
programme.desc: Varg ar en storslagen film om Klemens (Peter Stormare) och hans systerson Nejla som lever mitt i det norrlandska landskapet på gransen mellan Sverige och Norge.

programme.title: Skuggor i paradiset
programme.desc: Nikander ar en ensam sopbils-chauffor som en dag moter den anspråkslosa snabbkopskassorskan Ilona. programme.title: Bitchkram
programme.desc: Kristin raknar dagarna till studenten då hon antligen får lamna småstaden och sin manipulativa syster for sina drommars New York. Allt ar perfekt och lokaltidningen på orten har lovat att publicera Kristins kronikor om staden som aldrig sover. Men Kristin missar planet och gommer sig istallet hemma hos Andrea, en marklig ung tjej, långt ute på landet for att undvika total fornedring. I huset ingenstans tar Kristin med Andrea till New Yorks pulserande hjarta i ett vindlande virtuellt aventyr som alla darhemma kan folja i hennes artiklar. Men så tranger sig verkligheten på.

programme.title: Going To Kansas City
programme.desc: Kansas City, here we come” ropar Mikko (Mikko Nousiainen) nar han åker till Kansas City i USA som utbytesstudent. I stallet for storstad hamnar han andå till en småstad som heter Canaan, och dar ar frammande inte alltid valkomna. Mikko faller for vacker Carly Malone, dotter till stans forbittrad assisterande sheriff (Michael Ironside).

programme.desc: Efter sitt livs basta forestallning på Operan blir forstaviolinisten Siv Ellen Blad brutalt mordad. Kriminalkommissarie Cato Isaksen får snart veta att hon har utsatts for ett postrån. Finns det ett samband?

programme.title: Projekt Z
programme.desc: En grupp filmstudenter tar med sig tre lediga skådespelare till ett nedlagt hotell i de norska fjallen for att spela in en zombiefilm. Deras fiktion blir plotsligt verklighet nar en okand varelse borjar terrorisera filminspelningen.

programme.title: Bleeder
programme.desc: Louise alskar Leo djupt, hjartligt och unreservedly och lyckligtvis glad nar hon upptacker hon ar gravid. Men for Leo ar den oforutsedda graviditetsfallet, Det får koppen att stromma over. Barnet betyder ett bestamt farval for hans sista, glittrande hopp att bryta ut ur den sorgliga miljon och bli något.

programme.title: Kommissarie Spack
programme.desc: Kommissarie Mårten Spack har kallats till en brottsplats dar en kropp hittats genomborrade med knivar, gafflar, skedar och en hogaffel. Till allas forvåning drar Kommissarie Spack slutsatsen att det ror sig om ett sjalvmord. Spack ser kopplingar till andra sjalvmord och konstaterar att kåren fått en galen seriesjalvmordare på halsen. Han kommer snart på andra tankar nar hans råbarkade kollega Grunvald Karlsson hittar andra spår  något som leder till något storre an vad de kunnat ana. En ny kollega, superpolisen Irene Snusk kopplas in på fallet. Tillsammans ska trion losa ett av de viktigaste fallen i svensk kriminalhistoria.

programme.title: They Came Together
programme.desc: Nar Joel (Paul Rudd) och Molly (Amy Poehler) mottes var det hat vid forsta ogonkastet: hans storbolag Godiskompaniet hotade att stanga ner hennes bohemiska godisaffar. Plus att Joel fortfarande hade kanslor for sitt sexiga ex (Cobie Smulders). Men, trots allt så blir de kara, tills dess att de gor slut och Molly borjar dejta sin revisor (Ed Helms). Men, precis i sluttampen...tja, du får se helt enkelt. (Ledtråd: Joel håller ett stort tal och de hittar tillbaka till varandra.) Från regissoren som skapade Wet Hot American Summer, Wanderlust och Role Models kommer nu en helknapp och satirisk underminering av den romantiska komedigenren.

programme.title: Dubbelt begar
programme.desc: Dubbelt begar berattar historien om den unga kvinnan Chloe, som benagen till depression påborjar terapi och dar blir foralskad i sin psykoterapeut Paul. Efter ett par månader flyttar hon in hos sin nya alskare men upptacker snabbt att han doljer en del av sin identitet for henne.

programme.title: Programmet fortsatter strax
programme.desc: Vi tar igen vår skonhetssomn! Stanna kvar for mer prisvard underhållning utvald av Rakuten TV.

programme.title: All For Her
programme.desc: Devina och hennes man Rick langtar efter barn. Efter år av missfall blir Devina antligen gravid. Men det visar sig att hon lider av en dodlig sjukdom. Nu borjar en kamp mot klockan, Devina måste overleva tills barnet ar fott…

programme.title: Long Story Short
programme.desc: Det har ar berattelsen om Ellen och hennes vanner, och deras mer eller mindre sjalvforvållat komplicerade karleksliv och romantiska drommar. Tre år av vannernas basta och samsta karlekshistorier sammanfattas och berattas genom åtta kapitel, som alla utspelar sig vid olika festliga tillstallningar. Gruppen kampar med iden om det perfekta forhållandet och måste omvardera vad sann karlek egentligen ar.

programme.title: Warm Bodies
programme.desc: Karleken overvinner allt... till och med den oemotståndliga lusten att ata din alskades hjarnmassa! I en inte så avlagsen framtid ar jorden befolkad av lika delarmanniskoatande zombier och zombiebekampande manniskor. Men nar den unge zombien R plotsligt får impulsen att radda den varmblodiga flickan Julie från ett zombieoverfall borjar en vanskap som kommer att vanda upp och ner på nyavarldsordningen! Forutsatt att Julie kan hållasig levande – och R kan hålla sig levande dodtillrackligt lange!

programme.title: Patrick
programme.desc: Sarah Francis ar en ung kvinna vars liv ar lite rorigt. Det sista hon behover ar någon annan att ta hand om. Ändå har hennes farmor låtit henne arva en mycket bortskamd hund, Patrick – hennes mops. Sakert hade hon en tanke bakom det? Tydligen inte, eftersom denna fyrbenta forstorare orsakar kaos på alla upptankliga satt i Sarahs liv. Men hon inser snart att Patrick ar losningen på alla hennes problem. Trots att han också ar orsaken till många av dem.

programme.title: Equals
programme.desc: I en utopisk varld, dar våld och brott i princip ar utplånade via genetisk eliminering av kanslor, lever personer som Nia och Silas ett lugnt, handelselost och dronarlikt liv. De arbetar med att producera informationsmaterial på ett stort kontor och utvaxlar enbart artighetsfraser. Livet ar enkelt, anda till dess att ett rykte borjar florera: en sjukdom som orsakar att manniskor visar kanslor har brutit ut. Om det upptacks av overheten skickas de infekterade ivag, for att aldrig återvanda. Silas misstanker att han bar på sjukdomen och nar det bekraftas, blir han en paria. Trots det dras han till Nia, som också ar infekterad men har lyckats dolja symptomen battre an han sjalv.

programme.title: Griffin and Phoenix
programme.desc: Nar Griffin har fått diagnosen att han har dodlig cancer bestammer han sig for att ta livet i egna hander och ha lite kul innan han dor. Samtidigt som tiden for hans liv rinner ut traffar han och blir kar i Phoenix - som också har en hemlighet.

programme.title: Never Too Late
programme.desc: Fyra veteraner som overlevt Vietnamkrigets fånglager bestammer sig for att genomfora en sista flykt – från aldreboendet. Men att planera en rymning i ett senilt gang bjuder på utmaningar. Var och en bar på drommar, for vilka de ar beredda att satsa allt på detta sista hjaltedåd – om de bara kunde komma ihåg vad de skulle gora.

programme.title: Jack and Jill Vs. The World
programme.desc: Den framgångsrike chefen Jack (Freddie Prinze Jr.) ar en metodisk och kontrollerad man som arbetar på en ny reklambyrå på Manhattan. Under en rokpaus på kontorets hustak moter Jack skådespelerskan Jill som just anlant till New York for att soka jobb. Hon berattar om sin situation så Jack ordnar ett jobb åt henne i en reklamkampanj som hans byrå ligger bakom. Nar han sedan lamnar Jill vid hennes hem upptacker han att hon bor i ett nedgånget lågbudgethotell, så Jack erbjudar då henne att bo i hans gastrum så lange. Detta visar sig få konsekvenser som ingen kunnat ana...

programme.title: Loves Last Resort
programme.desc: Efter att ha dejtat i tio år har Chloes pojkvan Eric annu ite mognat till den man hon onskar han skulle vara. Hon hoppas skynda på forloppet genom att dumpa honom. Sex månader senare traffas de och Eric avslojar nyheten om att han ska gifta sig. For att komma bort tar hon semester och på samma semesterort dyker Eric med flickvan upp.

programme.title: Very Good Girls
programme.desc: New York-tjejerna Lily och Gerry ar basta vanner på det dar viset man bara ar som ung nar man har hela livet framfor sig. De gor upp en pakt om att forlora oskulden under den sista sommaren fore collegestudierna, men denna varma sommar satts deras vanskap for forsta gången på prov nar de råkar falla for en och samma kille. En oskuldsfull tid får sitt slut på fler an ett satt.

programme.title: If Only
programme.desc: En tragedi lar den unge engelska affarsmannen Ian Wyndham att satta karlek fore arbetet. Han lar sig antligen att oppna sig for sin sjalvstandiga flickvan Samantha Andrews.

programme.title: Love Hurts
programme.desc: Pauls kvinnoaffarer ersatts med flera komiska incidenter nar han måste tillbringa en helg med sina foraldrar, sin fore detta fru och barnen.

programme.title: The Dreamers
programme.desc: Tre cineaster – den amerikanske utbytesstudenten Matthew och tvillingparet Theo och Isabelle – har kommit varandra nara genom sitt gemensamma intresse. Matthew fascineras av Theo och Isabelles oortodoxt intima band. Nar tvillingarnas foraldrar reser bort en månad bjuds Matthew in att bo hos dem, och de forlorar sig i filmisk fantasi. The Dreamers ar ett romantiskt drama av Oscarsbelonade Bernardo Bertolucci, med Michael Pitt, Louis Garrel och Eva Green i huvudrollerna.

programme.title: Programmet fortsatter strax

programme.title: The Way You Look Tonight
programme.desc: Peter narmar sig 30 och ar fortfarande vilsen svulsten efter karlek med andlosa online dater utan resultat. En nyckfull date lamnar honom ensam i sangen en morgon nar han vaknar. Peter forsoker lamna allt bakom sig och fortsatter med nya dater från samma site. For varje date oppnas en helt ny varld av upplevelser och erfarenheter som får honom att ifrågasatta allt med naturkrafter, attraktion och akta karlek. Den stora frågan forblir obesvarad, kan Peter verkligen bli foralskad och hitta den akta karleken?

programme.title: Wingman, Inc
programme.desc: Bobby Tomkins jobbar som en professionell djurpsykolog och overtalats av sina vanner att praktisera sina fantastiska fardigheter som deras wingman bland tjejer. Och nar han antligen hittar sin egen efterlangtade karlek har han ingen aning om att Kristy ar hans absolut varsta tankbara rival. En ”man blocker” i varldsklass. Men i karlekens universum finns det inga spelregler, och enbart en av dem kan stå på tronen som nummer 1.

programme.title: Youth In Revolt
programme.desc: Michael Cera spelar rollen som Nick Twisp. En unik och alskvard tonåring med smak for livets sofistikerade gladjeamnen, såsom Sinatra och Fellini. På en campingsemester med familjen foralskar han sig i den vackra, intelligenta och frigjorda Sheeni Saunders (Portia Doubleday). Men geografi, familj och svartsjuka ex-partners konspirerar for att hålla Nick och Sheeni åtskilda. Efter uppmuntran från Sheeni overger Nick sitt tråkiga, forutsagbara liv och utvecklar ett rebelliskt alter ego: Francois Dillinger. Med mustasch, slips, djup rost och bad boy-attityd kan inget stoppa Francois från att vara tillsammans med Sheeni.

programme.title: The Last Kiss
programme.desc: Michael och Jenna ar ett par, och liksom alla andra 30-something-par står de infor en rad val i sitt forhållande. Men samtidigt som forpliktelserna blir allt fler, traffar Michael den unga skonheten Kim .

programme.title: All For Her
programme.desc: Devina och hennes man Rick langtar efter barn. Efter år av missfall blir Devina antligen gravid. Men det visar sig att hon lider av en dodlig sjukdom. Nu borjar en kamp mot klockan, Devina måste overleva tills barnet ar fott…

Forfattaren trodde att han skrev om framtiden, men i sjalva verket var det det forflutna. I hans roman åker ett tåg till 2046 lite då och då. Alla som åkte dit hade samma intention: att återuppleva sina forlorade minnen. Det sades att 2046 andrade sig aldrig något. Ingen visste sakert om det var sant, eftersom ingen som åkte dit någonsin hade kommit tillbaka - utom en. Han var dar. Han valde att åka darifrån. Han ville forandras.

programme.title: Cooking Up Love
programme.desc: Zoey hyr en matvagn och deltar i en reality-show på TV. Det går hett till mellan henne och den stilige grundaren till snabbmatskedjan, men nar Zoey får veta att han ar domare i tavlingen, blir det frasigt i pannan. Zoey ar fast besluten om att vinna rattvist och hon misstanker att "Mr-Too-Good-To-Be-True" ar ute efter hennes såsrecept och inte hennes hjarta.

programme.title: Albert Nobbs
programme.desc: Albert ar en forsynt man som doljer en stor hemlighet, han ar egentligen en kvinna som tvingats kla och bete sig som en man for att komma bort från fattigdom. En dag moter Albert en annan manniska i samma situation och han borjar dromma om ett liv i frihet utan hemligheter. Albert Nobbs ar en stark och rorande film med en stjarnspackad rollista.

Han traffar vackra kvinnor som kan tanka sig att låta en ”Toy Boy” bo i deras hem en kort tid i utbyte mot lite vilt och kravlost sex. Nick har koll på sitt liv och njuter av att vara uppvaktad av den framgångsrika advokaten Samantha (Anne Heche) tills han en dag traffar servitrisen Heather (Margarita Levieva) som spelar samma spel som han sjalv. Hon vill uppåt i varlden och plotsligt måste Nicki inse, att det kravs en del att ”forfora en forforare”.

programme.desc: This weekend sees the Strongman Champions League Log Lift World Championships in Lithuania. Big lifting names such as Graham Hicks , Vidas Blekaitis and Vytatus Lalas are in the startlist to push some big numbers.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S04 : E04 SCL 2017 Season 4, Episode 4, Holland
programme.desc: The battle of the Dutch will take place this edition in Lichtenvoorde, a place very well known in Holland because of the famous “Black Cross”. The athletes will compete over six heavy events and the winner gets 25 Strongman Champions League ranking points.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S04 : E05 SCL 2017 Season 4, Episode 5, Serbia
programme.desc: Set in the beautiful mountain resort Zlatibor, the fifth stage of the Strongman Champions League 2017 sees 14 athletes from across the world competing for the gold medal of SCL Serbia 2017. The event welcomes top-athlete - and odds-on favourite - Matjaz Belsak (Slovenia), who has presented himself in an impressive shape so far. Can his opponents defeat him?

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S04 : E06 SCL 2017 Season 4, Episode 6, Canada (Part 1)
programme.desc: The next two stages take place in Quebec. With eight events over two days, SCL Canada is a true ‘heavyweight’. The athletes compete in: Truck Pull, Deadlift with cars, Log Lift, and the Atlas Stones. The World’s Strongest Viking Jean-Francois Caron from Canada is a favourite, as well as current SCL leader Matjaz Belsak (Slovenia) and promising underdog Jimmy Paquet (Canada).

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S04 : E07 SCL 2017 Season 4, Episode 7, Canada (Part 2)
programme.desc: Welcome to the second day in Quebec. The athletes are fighting hard to win this two-day event. The last points of this SCL stage can be won over four outstanding disciplines: Power Stairs, Dumbbell Press, Keg Toss, and finally, the legendary Farmer’s Walk. Who will leave Canada with the yellow ‘Leader Shirt’?

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S04 : E08 SCL 2017 Season 4, Episode 8, Finland (Part 1)
programme.desc: Stages 8 and 9 of the SCL are hosted in Vaasa, Finland, taking place over a spectacular two-day event. After 3 wins so far, Matjaz Belsak from Slovenia plans to extend his lead at the top of the table. Among the other 13 highly motivated strongmen, two SCL legends will make their comeback to the competition: Former World Champion of 2015, Krzysztof Radzikowski (Poland) and Dainis Zageris (Latvia).

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S04 : E09 SCL 2017 Season 4, Episode 9, Finland (Part 2)
programme.desc: The fight for the Finnish trophy continues. In this unmissable SCL event, the strongmen battle for the win in the Carry and Drag, the Forward Hold, Deadlifting with Cars and the Loading Race. Belsak, Radzikowski and Zageris look good after the first day, but the others haven’t given up yet.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S04 : E10 SCL 2017 Season 4, Episode 10, Finland Lightweight World Championship
programme.desc: This under 105kg category event is the ultimate preparation for up-and-coming strongman athletes before entering the heavy class. The Lightweight World Championship is a special every year in the SCL calendar as it sees new talents rise and many promising athletes who are gearing up for future tournaments. A total of 25 athletes from 16 different countries make their way to Kokkola, Finland

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S04 : E11 SCL 2017 Season 4, Episode 11, Romania
programme.desc: Situated in the very heart of the Carpathian Mountains, Sibiu is a Romanian town where the climate is pleasantly mild, offering some of the best weather conditions for a strongman event around Europe. All this, without doubt, set the mood for the high results and showtime vibes in Stage 11 of Strongman Champions League. The competition in Sibiu was organized in six different disciplines

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S04 : E12 SCL 2017 Season 4, Episode 12, Curacao
programme.desc: From now on every stage of these series will be more than crucial. Curacao is a beautiful Dutch island in the Caribbean, with a great atmosphere to hold another stage of the MLO Strongman Champions League. Let’s see who takes the title here and who will secure a place in the next stage.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S04 : E13 SCL 2017 Season 4, Episode 13, Jordan
programme.desc: Ten of the world’s strongest men gathered in Amman to compete in Jordan’s first-ever Truck-Pull Championship. The contestants race against the clock while pulling a 21-ton truck across the track. One of the most fierce competitors to take part in the event was four-time winner of the World’s Strongest Man competition, Brian Shaw.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S04 : E14 SCL 2017 Season 4, Episode 14, Greece
programme.desc: Taking place in Corinth, Greece, considered by many the cradle of the sports competition games, an epic strongman battle will mark the last stage before the upcoming big two-day season’s finale in Chetumal, Mexico. In front of more than 5000 spectators, the twelve athletes compete in Log Lifts, Card Deadlift, Conan’s Wheel and Loading.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S04 : E15 SCL 2017 Season 4, Episode 15, Mexico World Finals (Part 1)
programme.desc: The first day of the two-part finale sees the strongest men competing in Carry and Drag, Dumbbell Lift and the Truck Pull. Everything is possible in this heated fight for the crown against the backdrop of stunning Chetumal, Mexico.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S04 : E16 SCL 2017 Season 4, Episode 16, Mexico World Finals (Part 2)
programme.desc: On the second day of the grand finale of the 2017 Strongman Champions League, the athletes have a last chance to secure the medals in the spectacular four events Weight for Height, Deadlift Cars, Forward Hold and The Loading Medley. Be prepared for stunning performances – and even world records!

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S05 : E01 SCL 2018 Season 5, Episode 1, Norway - World Strongest Viking
programme.desc: Season 2018 begins with 14 strongest men in the world, all competing for the title. The competition kicks off in Norway. We’ll see typical Viking disciplines, team events and world records in heavy conditions in the land of snow and ice. They will suffer, they will freeze and fight in this first competition of the year for the title that they will carry on their shoulders throughout whole year.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S05 : E02 SCL 2018 Season 5, Episode 2, Germany - FIBO Power
programme.desc: The next stop in strongest league of the world is muscle capital, largest number of strong shoulders per capichampions league on the planet. It’s a FIBO - the biggest expo on planet Earth and the second stage of 2018 Strongman champions league, in Cologne, Germany.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S05 : E03 SCL 2018 Season 5, Episode 3, Abu Dhabi
programme.desc: For the first time in history, Strongman Champions League will set up competition in Abu Dhabi. The line-up of super athletes, who are part of the SCL, includes former world champions Dainis Zageris (Latvia) and Krzysztof Radzikowski (Poland), current world champion Matjaz Belsak (Slovenia) and biggest strongman in the World Sean O’Hagan (Ireland).

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S05 : E04 SCL 2018 Season 5, Episode 4, Holland (Part 1)
programme.desc: Strongman classic in land where there is no place for anything else excepts strength, fight and endurance. Here are fourteen of the strongest men, fighting for the title of strongest in Holland.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S05 : E05 SCL 2018 Season 5, Episode 5, Holland (Part 2)
programme.desc: We go back to Holland, where former champion Dainis Zageris is in leading position after the first three events. Alongside Radzikowski, he is in this moment favorite for world title, and also leader shirt holder.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S05 : E06 SCL 2018 Season 5, Episode 6, Finland
programme.desc: Stage six of Strongman champions league, 2018 is set back on north, in Finland. Here we have Matjaz Belsak, wearing SCL leader shirt, one of the biggest strongman in the World Mika Torro, fan favorite strongman in all over the World – Will Baggott, and also big name from Baltic – Aivars Smaukstelis

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S05 : E07 SCL 2018 Season 5, Episode 7, Serbia
programme.desc: Twelve strongman, including defending Worldchampion Matjaz Belsak from Slovenia , will compete on “Air spa” for the title of best in homeland country of Tesla, Pupin, Novak Djokovic. Matjaz Belsak is the SCL leader in this competition, chasing his third victory this season.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S05 : E08 SCL 2018 Season 5, Episode 8, Finland - U105 (Part 1)
programme.desc: The World championship in lightweights of the Strongman Champions League bring to us 50 strongmen from all over the world. All athletes are under 105 kilograms and for them this is the step up to the ultimate heavyweights.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S05 : E09 SCL 2018 Season 5, Episode 9, Finland - U105 (Part 2)
programme.desc: In this second stage of the World championship of lightweights we will find out who out of the 12 athletes will win the title in the under 105 kilogram category.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S05 : E10 SCL 2018 Season 5, Episode 10, Romania (Part 1)
programme.desc: The first part of SCL Romania 2018 will be hosted in Brasov. This episode features a new event for Strongman Champion League: “ The Chopper Pull”!

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S05 : E11 SCL 2018 Season 5, Episode 11, Romania (Part 2)
programme.desc: After three classical Strongman events – Dead lift, Loading and Front hold – and one historical, Chopper Pull for the first time in history of Strongman, now we go to find out who will take title in Romania. This is the second stage in Romania and it remains to be seen who will win the title; Aivars, Travis or Krzyzstof?

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S05 : E12 SCL 2018 Season 5, Episode 12, Curacao (Part 1)
programme.desc: The next destination of Strongman Champions League is in a piece of paradise on earth – Curacao. We bring to you some special Strongman events like the Rock Lift, Tug of War and Weight for Height in this episode.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S05 : E13 SCL 2018 Season 5, Episode 13, Curacao (Part 2)
programme.desc: This is the last competition before the grand finals. After the first three events Zageris is in top place, but can O’Hagan, Baggott, Petursson and Ortmayer step into the final? Last chance some of them will find through events like Forward Hold, Truck Pull, Dead Lift and loading very big objects.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S05 : E14 SCL 2018 Season 5, Episode 14, Road to Mexico
programme.desc: We bring you 50 minutes of Strongman inside. Fears, inspiration, courage, the best and worst from our finalists and their expectation of the finals. We also go to Poland and Germany to represent one day in the training of Krzysztof Radzikowski and Dennis Kohlruss. See all the finalists for Mexico in their comfort zone here, with their backgrounds /motivations /family and friends.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S05 : E15 SCL 2018 Season 5, Episode 15, Mexico - World Finals (Part 1)
programme.desc: The first part of the Strongman Champions League 2018 finals in Mexico. The last twelve athletes all pushing their boundaries and testing their limits to take the World title.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S05 : E16 SCL 2018 Season 5, Episode 16, Mexico - World Finals (Part 2)
programme.desc: After 11 months and 14 competitions all over the world, it all comes down to the final in this episode. The strongmen must show their best skills and every mistake is expensive, so their concentration must be at the highest possible level. Will Krzysztof manage to take off back or will Dainis maintain his lead?

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S06 : E01 SCL 2019 Season 6, Episode 1, World Strongest Viking
programme.desc: This year 14 athletes from all over the world came to Fefor to compete in 6 cruel events. Well see typical Viking disciplines on very heavy conditions in land of snow and ice, World records and athletes like the title defender Krzysztof Radzikowski, strongest guys from Holland and Germany and many more

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S06 : E02 SCL S6 Ep2 FIBO Power
programme.desc: The next stop in strongest league of the world is muscle capital, largest number of strong shoulders per capita in the World and of course, the most powerful host in Strongman champions league on the planet. It’s a FIBO - the biggest expo on planet Earth and the second stage of 2019 Strongman champions league, in Cologne, Germany.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S06 : E03 SCL 2019 Season 6, Episode 3, Turkey
programme.desc: On a spectacular beach in Alanya, the MLO Strongman Champions League Turkey was viewed by thousands of spectators over a two day battle. With 12 athletes at the start over 6 cruel events, like Marble Stone Lift, Truckpull and Deadlift cars. And with the comeback of Travis Ortmayer / USA, former stone king and world ranked competitor. Winner of several SCL stages in the past.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S06 : E04 SCL 2019 Season 6, Episode 4, Holland (Part 1)
programme.desc: Four times Strongest Man of Holland, Alex Moonen and the “Flying Dutchman” Kelvin de Ruiter competing here in Holland against 12 other strongest men in the world. There were 6 events in total, and 3 in this episode: The first event, a truckpull of 17.000 kg over 25 meters in max 75 seconds, was a real hard pull Also for the World Champion Truckpull, Holland’s runner-up Kelvin de Ruiter, but watch his amazing technique here.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S06 : E05 SCL 2019 Season 6, Episode 5, Holland (Part 2)
programme.desc: Strongest Man of Holland, Alex Moonen and the “Flying Dutchman” Kelvin de Ruiter, competing in Holland against 12 other strongest men in the world. There were 6 events in total, 3 in this second episode; a Viking-press of 150 kg with the current world record holder Luke Herrick. The fifth event, a front hold of 25 kg is loved or hated by the athletes and lastly, the Stones of Strength.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S06 : E06 SCL 2019 Season 6, Episode 6, Russia
programme.desc: An unbelievable TANK PULL of 50.000 kg was at the stage of SCL RUSSIA. Never seen this before! Not only a tank pull was done here but also the Viking Press/ Deadlift Max and Log lift reps were spectacular events to see here in Russia. With Mikhail Koklyaev also as event presenter, the former top 3 world strongest man from Russia was there

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S06 : E07 SCL 2019 Season 6, Episode 7, Serbia
programme.desc: In this year’s edition on The Balkan Peninsula, we have competing the new talent from Estonia Marko Remlik together with Sebastian Kurek from Poland and yellow leader Kelvin de Ruiter

programme.sub-title: S03 : E08 Top Million Dollar Agent
programme.desc: Tomarra and Rob had just married and blended their two families. As a new family, they want to transition to a quiet neighbourhood away from the hustle and bustle of Toronto. Steve is up for the challenge. Rob is a writer and plans to work from home, while Tomarra is a naturopath who would love to have her own studio. Ultimately, they want to start cherishing the real things in life, and that is spending more time with their kids.

programme.title: Top Million Dollar Agent
programme.sub-title: S03 : E09 Top Million Dollar Agent
programme.desc: Darlene and Bruce are in the market for a new home and have enlisted Laura to help them out. Darlenes one request is that they stay close to their current home, where their daughter goes to school. For Bruce, quality construction materials and workmanship are of paramount importance. One thing the entire family agrees on is that the backyard should have a fantastic entertainment space since they spend plenty of time together outdoors and enjoy having guests over.

programme.title: Top Million Dollar Agent
programme.sub-title: S03 : E10 Top Million Dollar Agent
programme.desc: Kathryn and Neil are true urbanites. They love what downtown Toronto has to offer. When Neil found out his company was relocating to Guelph, they werent thrilled. After five months of long commutes, the Thompson family is ready to take the risk and make a move-with some conditions. The new house has to have a pool and playroom for the kids and a large entertainment area for adults. Eves challenge is to find them an enticing home that will convince their friends from the city to visit.

programme.title: Top Million Dollar Agent
programme.sub-title: S03 : E12 Top Million Dollar Agent
programme.desc: Stephanie is making a big move from BC to Guelph to be closer to her son John and his family. She doesnt want the move to be a hassle and is looking for an accessible, decent-sized home for her grandchildren and visitors from BC. Good sized guest rooms and a large backyard are a must. As she loves to cook, she would also like a new kitchen. Eve will show Stephanie 3 beautiful homes that fit the criteria. Stephanie is going to have a difficult decision.

programme.title: Top Million Dollar Agent
programme.sub-title: S03 : E13 Top Million Dollar Agent
programme.desc: Steve Bailey, Mike Donia and Daryl King review their favourite homes. Steve takes us down memory lane to his 18th century farmhouse, and another home with a stunning infinity pool. Daryls listings range from King city to Caloden, with helicopter pads and sprawling backyards. Mike brings us back to his fabulous listings in Thailand. He shows us a home made entirely of Bamboo, and billion-dollar property.

Daryl knows all about tranquility and goes golfing with Mike to discuss his client and Mikes listing for them.

Mike is the perfect agent for this couple because he lives, eats, and breathes the luxury lifestyle.

Daryls client has older children with their own families now so they are looking for a home with lots of land and nature. It is very important to them because they want to be able to have everyone comfortably visit and eventually retire here in a few years.

Jins client lives a very active and busy lifestyle so they require somewhere with low maintenance but still has enough space for a big family. Inez takes Jin to her hair stylist Anastasia for some business and pleasure.

programme.title: Top Million Dollar Agent
programme.sub-title: S01 : E08 Top Million Dollar Agent
programme.desc: Moving in together can be stressful but fun because you are starting a new life together!
